blog.name: angelofberlin2000
blog.title: Like a Rose trampled on the ground
blog.description:
In addition to the pain and the exhaustion, he recalled how waiting on the cross between takes became tedious. To fight the boredom, he listened to music on headphones. One particular song called "Above All" (Like a Rose ...) by Michael W. Smith helped him through his most difficult moments.

"It arrived when I was confused and angry. I didn't think I could go on. The song described how Jesus was rejected and alone. That thought took me to a place — it opened an interior door that held me while on the cross," an emotional Caviezel explained. "The experience of feeling rejected and alone as all those around me laughed while drinking their hot coffees, oblivious to what was occurring. Jesus must have felt like this — forsaken, rejected, alone, and despised. It helped me pray in a very deep way — to pray without words, to pray from the heart. The discomfort, the loneliness, the split shoulder, the raw flesh all forced me into the arms of God because I had nowhere else to go for a performance I knew I was unable to create."
Jim Caviezel, Shamelessly Catholic

title: Bill & Ted Face the Music מקבל תאריך יציאה רשמי
body:
Bill & Ted Face the Music מקבל תאריך יציאה רשמי

Bill & Ted Face the Music, הסרט שלישי בכותר ביל וטד האהוב, מקבל תאריך רשמי מפי השחקנים עצמם

תחשבו על צמדים אייקונים בהיסטוריית הקולנוע, וינסנט וג’ולס מ”ספרות זולה” או הארי ולויד מ”טיפשים בלי הפסקה” תמיד בין הראשונים שנזכרים בהם, אבל אם אנחנו מחפשים את הצמד שהגדיר את תחילת שנות התשעים על המסך הגדול, אלו ללא ספק הצמד של ביל וטד. קיאנו ריבס ואלכס וינטר לקחו אותנו לשתי הרפתקאות מצוינות ב-1989 ולכן זה…

Custom Palette, I used the 9 colours nyx one with the colours: STFU, Turnt Up, Pink Cloud, Wild Orchid, LOL,...
body:
Bill and Ted Palette!!! How to make:

You will need:

  1. Custom Palette, I used the 9 colours nyx one with the colours: STFU, Turnt Up, Pink Cloud, Wild Orchid, LOL, Maneater, Moon Rock, Whipped Cream and Bad Seed.
  2. Glue. I used Mod Podge, but PVA or Spray Mount should work as well!
  3. The cover and colour names (you can make your own, but these are mine if you want to use them)

Assembling the palette is easy, just glue the cover on the outside and the colour names on the inside! The eyeshadows slot straight into the empty palette.

Cost:

It’s pretty cheap. I’ll assume you have glue and paper, so I’ll just list the make up prices :)

  • NYX Custom Pro Palette - £5 (roughly $6.50)
  • NYX Hot Singles Shadow Refills £2.50 each, £22.50 for nine (roughly $3.25, roughly $29.24 for nine)

Enjoy!
